http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/Decomposed-body-of-woman-found/article14026298.ece

A decomposed body of woman aged about 25 was found in a sugarcane field near Kilpennathur.Balaraman, a farmer of Chinna Kangiyanur village was irrigating his sugarcane field past Wednesday midnight. As he felt the stench of dead body he searched through the field and found a decomposed body of woman wearing rose colour chudidhar. Kilpennathur police are investigating to find out who the woman was.They suspect it to be a murder and the murderer could have thrown the body into the sugarcane field.